ygData.messageBody:
I am Justene Thyme. I had once guy flirting with me in the Nexus. I've heard of people meeting people through EQ, meeting in RL, than living together. I've had 4 sets of EQ friends do this in RL. With my luck I'd end up in prison for meeting a minor (I have a BF and he's 30 I'm 25 in RL). I have an 8 year old son so in view with "mother eyes" I can't do it. One guy flirted with my main for a long time (Alexandrah) saying he's buying a house, I seem like a great person, and so on... but I left it as flirting.
 
In RL I completed Microcomputer Operations and I'm returning next month for Computer Programming. People say I'm intelligent but I'm normal in my eyes like any other person. I have many hobbies... my best activity is my family.
 
Bev--
